Students really enjoyed Professor Holtzman’s company and found him to be “knowledgeable,” “engaging,” and “effective.” One student said Professor Holtzman “led great discussions and consistently held the class’ attention.” Another student reported Professor Holtzman “always makes everything so interesting.”&#8232;&#8232;

